<figureCitation box="[518,627,572,598]" captionStart-0="Fig" captionStart-1="Fig" captionStartId-0="12.[189,232,1887,1913]" captionStartId-1="13.[189,232,1892,1918]" captionTargetBox-0="[189,1398,431,1848]" captionTargetBox-1="[254,1324,265,1854]" captionTargetId-0="figure-47@12.[189,1398,425,1848]" captionTargetId-1="figure-15@13.[254,1334,265,1854]" captionTargetPageId-0="12" captionTargetPageId-1="13" captionText-0="Fig. 7. Eusarcus xambioa sp. nov., ♂, holotype (ISLA 60386), habitUs. A. Dorsal view. B. Ventral view. C. Lateral view. Scale bars: A–B = 1 mm; C = 0.5 mm." captionText-1="Fig. 8. Eusarcus xambioa sp. nov., ♂, holotype (ISLA 60386). A–B. Femur IV, dorsal and ventral view, respectively. C–D. Femur III, dorsal and ventral view, respectively. E–F. Patella and tibia IV, dorsal and ventral view, respectively. G–H. Patella and tibia III, dorsal and ventral view, respectively. I– J. Detail of trochanter IV, dorsal and ventral view, respectively. Scale bars: A–H = 0.5 mm; I–J = 0.2 mm." figureDoi-0="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4628985" figureDoi-1="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4628987" httpUri-0="https://zenodo.org/record/4628985/files/figure.png" httpUri-1="https://zenodo.org/record/4628987/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="51">Figs 7–8</figureCitation>
). Body and appendages background colour Deep Orange Yellow (69), appendages Strong Orange Yellow (68).
</paragraph>
